A photograph of a woman holding up a wooden picture frame, obscuring her face, standing in a field of wildflowers at sunset. The frame contains the abstract retro floral art print in earthy tones (terracotta, mustard yellow, dusty pink, brown) seen in image_17.png. The woman is wearing a pleated white skirt. The late afternoon sun casts warm golden light and soft, long shadows across the field, creating a dreamy, natural atmosphere. The central text "FRAME MOCKUP" is completely removed, showing only the clear art print within the frame. The circular logo text "DIN STANDARD RATIOS..." and the bottom text "BY INFINITY MOCKUP LAB" are also removed for a clean image.

[Technical Detail]:
Professional photography with a Hasselblad X2D 100C, extremely high resolution, sharp focus, natural color science, architectural interior style, clean minimalist rendering, 8k resolution.
